Package horsentp.display

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Displayable
    A common interface that tells the Displayer how to display something
    DisplayCanvas
    A common interface for things that Displayer can draw upon.
    DisplayLink
    Implementing DisplayLink provides a way to say where it will be drawn.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisplayConfiguration  
    Displayer
    This is an important object in this framework because it is the "remote control" to all things rendering.
    DisplayLayer  
    ImageDisplay
    Allows an image to be drawn by the Displayer.
